446
00:35:39,637 --> 00:35:40,555
Kumusta?

447
00:35:40,638 --> 00:35:43,891
Hoy, Kang Ro-bin, nasaan ka?
Nanood ka ba ng Oddball noon?

448
00:35:43,975 --> 00:35:48,771
Nababaliw na ang may-ari ng Hearty House
Hinahanap ka at si Chae-ni!

449
00:35:52,692 --> 00:35:54,485
Ako ang lola ni Eun Chae-ni.

450
00:36:09,083 --> 00:36:09,959
Sige lang.

451
00:36:10,459 --> 00:36:12,503
Gusto kitang makita sandali.

452
00:36:13,713 --> 00:36:15,173
